      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To establish a broadband infrastructure finance and innovation program to make available loans, loan guarantees, and lines of credit for the construction and deployment of broadband infrastructure, and for other purposes.</title>
